The Keiser Report  No. 131
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 22 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


Build More Reactors, Not!

This time Max and Stacy report on the bright side of inflation and nuclear meltdown and examine Saif al Islam Gaddafis allegations that President Sarkozy owes him money. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to Business Insider's Joe Weisenthal about being a paper bug for dollars, yen and central banking. <a href="
